y this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 9:54 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 21:54 UTC\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776203663125,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"5f84b24e\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"I need to check the sessions_list to find active master-orchestrator sessions, then compile a status report and send it to the Lead.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_dxgumli5gbgm_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"kinds\": [\n                  \"agent\"\n                ],\n                \"limit\": 20,\n                \"activeMinutes\": 120,\n                \"messageLimit\": 2\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 345,\n            \"output\": 90,\n            \"totalTokens\": 14284,\n            \"cacheRead\": 10789,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 3060,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776203663330,\n          \"responseId\": \"062dea90288d29e66a9c8e2bcb17730f\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"490d7099\",\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"hea