l completed or terminated sessions mixed in—some older cron jobs and subagents that have finished, including a few failures from earlier today.\\n\\nLooking at the current state compared to the baseline from 21:37 UTC, everything's holding steady: the QLHV monitor is still running, the Agent Status cron is stable, the DTLX 5p session completed and restarted as expected, and the Telegram group remains active. There's one additional session from master-orchestrator that appears to be a new heartbeat poll, which is normal cycling. The overall system health looks solid with no significant deviations from what was baseline.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Silent. All sessions stable vs last baseline (21:37 UTC): QLHV cron running ✅, DTLX cron cycling normally ✅, Agent Status running ✅, group session running, no failures. No state changes.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 26587,\n            \"output\": 385,\n            \"totalTokens\": 41431,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 515,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776203606316,\n          \"responseId\": \"062dea57fc278401bb4bb4b80188f243\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"357471d2\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n        \"to\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1